 SELECT COUNT(*), JOB FROM EMP GROUP BY JOB;

  COUNT(*) JOB
---------- ---------
         4 CLERK
         4 SALESMAN
         1 PRESIDENT
         3 MANAGER
         2 ANALYST

2. Write a query to display the lowest salary for each job.
 SELECT MIN(SAL), JOB FROM EMP GROUP BY JOB ;

  MIN(SAL) JOB
---------- ---------
       800 CLERK
      1250 SALESMAN
      5000 PRESIDENT
      2450 MANAGER
      3000 ANALYST

